item.title: back in Japan
item.description: 08:30 Friday 05 April 2019 JST Back in Japan as of Wednesday and still a bit jet lagged. Today I plan to call AB and get back in the groove with them. I have been reading Urbit docs and considering starting one of my planets on my local machine here. Gotta get that figured out before I try to start my star, ~wanbus. Lesson in Akihabara was fine last night.
